description: Lists all tags on an Amazon DocumentDB resource.

parameters.name: ResourceName
parameters.description: The Amazon DocumentDB resource with tags to be listed. This value is an Amazon Resource Name (ARN).

parameters.name: Filters
parameters.description: This parameter is not currently supported. (dict) --- A named set of filter values, used to return a more specific list of results. You can use a filter to match a set of resources by specific criteria, such as IDs. Wildcards are not supported in filters. The name of the filter. Filter names are case sensitive. One or more filter values. Filter values are case sensitive. (string) ---

nested_params.name: Name
nested_params.description: The name of the filter. Filter names are case sensitive.

nested_params.name: Values
nested_params.description: One or more filter values. Filter values are case sensitive.

nested_items.name: TagList
nested_items.description: A list of one or more tags.

nested_items.name: Key
nested_items.description: The required name of the tag. The string value can be from 1 to 128 Unicode characters in length and can't be prefixed with ' aws:' or ' rds:'. The string can contain only the set of Unicode letters, digits, white space, --_', --.', --/', --=', --+', ---' (Java regex: '^([\p{L}\p{Z}\p{N}_.:/=+\-]*)$').

nested_items.name: Value
nested_items.description: The optional value of the tag. The string value can be from 1 to 256 Unicode characters in length and can't be prefixed with ' aws:' or ' rds:'. The string can contain only the set of Unicode letters, digits, white space, --_', --.', --/', --=', --+', ---' (Java regex: '^([\p{L}\p{Z}\p{N}_.:/=+\-]*)$').
